beer.beer_description:
Every year a festival asks breweries to produce one off limited beers to pour on their container bar and then asks to embargo the beer from sales until the festival is finished.
Well this year we said Yeah, Nah and have decided to release to you the consumer first.
Its an Imperial Marshmallow and hazelnut Porter based on the US treat a S’mores
So sit around the campfire or don’t and enjoy this take on a S’mores biscuit.
